{"tid":163076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人豬合一？】誓讓人類移植豬器官，基因改造初創獲3800萬美元融資","createTime":"2017-03-19T17:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T17:02:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3afe0c652238b56bdcd3b7da2dea5af28f700b35","tid":163076,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1000X52537-810x425.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F1000X52537-810x425.png&h=af5fdf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">主要利用基因改造工具CRISPR去讓豬器官成為適合移植到人類身上的科研初創Egenesis日前成功獲得3800萬美元融資。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by eGenesis<br />\n<br />\n這間在2015年成立的科創由哈佛科學家George Church以及有「北大才女 」 之稱的楊璐菡共同創辦，致力研究把豬器官中令人類感到不適的基因，使其適合移植到人類身上。<br />\n<br />\n是次融資由Biomatics Capital以及創投基金ARCH主領，投資者更包括投資基金Khosla、Alta Partners、Alexandria Equities、Heritage Provider Network以及匿名投資者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Nasco<br />\n<br />\n楊透露，目前要成功將動物器官移植到人體身上則需要克服兩大障礙。第一障礙為病毒學上的障礙。由於豬器官的一些基因先天帶有能傳播疾病到人體的病毒，胡亂移植到人體身上則會使接受移植者感染病毒。第二為免疫學上的障礙。移植器官到人體之後，人體本身的免疫系統就會排斥這外來的器官，引發其他連鎖效應。運用CRISPR，Egenesis就能克服這些前人不能克服的障礙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/03/17/article/22648/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2Farticle%2F22648%2F&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=61fc870d\" target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/03/17/article/22648/</a>"},{"pid":"3cc856b96e66a321597b7372c35ff1930690ad87","tid":163076,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1000X52537-810x425.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F1000X52537-810x425.png&h=af5fdf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n邊個移植俾邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0a5f0f15a7d1ecbee5281cb6b5fba7026fcf4f","tid":163076,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"人頭豬腦不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179042eae9b0a8963d2ede2507fcdf5a0dd8f989","tid":163076,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27ea69e87e4f0730b1f8226d4c55e406275c91e","tid":163076,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:12:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ff02f8fc9c61b0a2293e136a6c7c51cc81a34b1","tid":163076,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:29:58.000Z","msg":"食得又用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e37d282756896bc19dedd72e76b8989e3076ab","tid":163076,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"唔係幾接受到"},{"pid":"c0b308bd96b80b64e433ae5750cf2bbf47350f1e","tid":163076,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"瑞士山區豬肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111d36d91bf68aa5b1c87994e360a52dada9e370","tid":163076,"uid":87517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:08:30.000Z","msg":"港豬本身咪人豬合一"},{"pid":"7e1f2fc70c7ef998547329d9377e133ab5319a7f","tid":163076,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"